{"id":438477,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/05/【立此存照】党章是最好的胎教/","date":"2016-05-20T07:56:48Z","modified":"2016-05-20T07:56:48Z","title":"【立此存照】党章是最好的胎教","content":"<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://freeweibo.com/en/weibo/3977199264701543\" target=\"_blank\">@李方平律师</a>：【新疆、云南干部异口同声：党章是最好的胎教】“党章党规是最好的胎教”，怀二胎4月参加竞赛的（云南）陇川县防震减灾局副局长李擎说。新疆医科大一附院党办三孕妇也是如此说…</p></blockquote>\n<div id=\"attachment_438478\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/6a80bfcdgw1f41s4j5hr3j20m80ci76p.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-438478\"><img class=\"wp-image-438478\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/6a80bfcdgw1f41s4j5hr3j20m80ci76p.jpg\" alt=\"6a80bfcdgw1f41s4j5hr3j20m80ci76p\" width=\"550\" height=\"309\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/6a80bfcdgw1f41s4j5hr3j20m80ci76p.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/6a80bfcdgw1f41s4j5hr3j20m80ci76p-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/6a80bfcdgw1f41s4j5hr3j20m80ci76p-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">来源：自由微博</span></p></div>\n<p><em>背景新闻：</em></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://www.jjjc.yn.gov.cn/info-87-18990.html\" target=\"_blank\">德宏州纪委｜德宏：举办党章党规知识竞赛6名厅级11名处级领导干部带队上阵参赛</a></strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/45038600317fdb48c6b15fc97e499bda_thumb.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-438480\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-438480\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/45038600317fdb48c6b15fc97e499bda_thumb.jpg\" alt=\"45038600317fdb48c6b15fc97e499bda_thumb\" width=\"475\" height=\"315\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/45038600317fdb48c6b15fc97e499bda_thumb.jpg 536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/45038600317fdb48c6b15fc97e499bda_thumb-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 475px) 100vw, 475px\" /></a><br />\n就此次党章党规知识竞赛，参赛选手如何评价和准备呢？[&#8230;]“为参加此次知识竞赛，我每天空余时间都在学党章党规，走路、吃饭、坐车在记，连晚上睡觉时也在背，自身的党章党规意识得到了较大的提升。”参赛的梁河县副县长郑瑜告诉笔者。“<strong>党章党规是最好的胎教</strong>”<strong>怀二胎4月参加竞赛的陇川县防震减灾局副局长李擎说。</strong></p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>另附：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://freeweibo.com/en/weibo/3976430322970735\" target=\"_blank\">@互联网的那点事</a>：有些行业就是反应迅速，值得学习！</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/6106a4f0gw1f3zbtdj14ej20qo0zkdii.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-438479\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-438479\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/6106a4f0gw1f3zbtdj14ej20qo0zkdii.jpg\" alt=\"6106a4f0gw1f3zbtdj14ej20qo0zkdii\" width=\"425\" height=\"567\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/6106a4f0gw1f3zbtdj14ej20qo0zkdii.jpg 960w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/6106a4f0gw1f3zbtdj14ej20qo0zkdii-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/6106a4f0gw1f3zbtdj14ej20qo0zkdii-768x1024.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 425px) 100vw, 425px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[30078,18804,25917,9375,31061,20162,11848]}